snippet.textDisplay:
It's a freestyle because those were the thoughts that came to his head off the top upon hearing the beat. He probably wrote them on his phone so he won't forget.
With regular tracks, artists tend to come up with the lyrics without a beat yet or with beats without lyrics yet. Like when they're sleeping, or taking a shit, or in the shower etc.
So yes, it's a freestyle, he heard the beat and these are the thoughts he came up with for a one-take. A regular track could take days and weeks, changing of lyrics, verses etc.
